ral world.”","targetRectangle":{"y":662.64715051651001,"x":128.42203521728516,"width":1599.0720000000001,"height":57.3038330078125}},{"text":"As a result GYRE’s gallery is the perfect place to house Alejandro’s, “One With Nature” December 2026 exhibition.","targetRectangle":{"y":749.64715051651001,"x":128.42203521728516,"width":1171.5840000000014,"height":28.3038330078125}},{"text":"With annual visitor numbers ranging between 190,000 and 200,000, with December being the highest volume of traffic during the year.","targetRectangle":{"y":807.64715051651001,"x":128.42203521728516,"width":1386.7680000000009,"height":28.3038330078125}},{"text":"Young, 25-35 male and female shoppers both Japanese and inbound with expendable income make up the vibrant traffic both shopping and restaurant activity.","targetRectangle":{"y":865.64715051651001,"x":128.42203521728516,"width":1644.384,"height":28.3038330078125}},{"text":"logo_k (1).svg","targetRectangle":{"y":960.9208984375,"x":62.0703125,"width":155.16172790527344,"height":77.763412475585938}},{"text":"logo_CHANEL.svg","targetRectangle":{"y":53.978702545166016,"x":1060.8165283203125,"width":288.97576332092285,"height":72.533363342285156}},{"text":"logo_Maison-Margiela.svg","targetRectangle":{"y":155.7906494140625,"x":1060.8164978027344,"width":331.21875,"height":96.25}},{"text":"visvim-logo-png_seeklogo-593586.png","targetRectangle":{"y":270.76054382324219,"x":1066.4259033203125,"width":300.78929901123047,"height":84.09375}},{"text":"600x600.v2-2.svg","targetRectangle":{"y":388.66861724853516,"x":1080.1803512573242,"width":214.65625,"height":96.25}},{"text":"logo_PLAY.svg","targetRectangle":{"y":491.31031799316406,"x":1465.5289611816406,"width":206.85220956802368,"height":114.0625}},{"text":"AZUMA FARM - AML-ART at GYRE GALLERY, OMOTESANDO","targetRectangle":{"y":970.69948899745941,"x":622.41821670532227,"width":688.72800000000007,"height":28.4239501953125}}],"baseLayer":{"animations":[],"initialState":{"affineTransform":[1,0,0